criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Speak/read English;

          -  Currently provide care-giving support (e.g. emotional, social, physical, task-related)
             to an adult over the age of 65;

          -  Currently provide care-giving support at least 2 hours per week (e.g. may include
             grocery shopping, scheduling appointments, and transportation);

          -  Currently involved in any decision-making related to the healthcare and support of
             this adult over the age of 65;

          -  Score >2 on the 8-item Informant Interview to Differentiate Aging and Dementia (AD8);
             and

          -  Access to and the ability to use the internet to complete a series of online
             activities

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Less than 21 years old

          -  Unable to speak and read English
